<![CDATA[<div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">attention which may affect your children.</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of hand, foot and mouth disease in a&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">pupil in one of our Reception classes. Hand, foot and mouth disease is a contagious, viral infection&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">which spreads if contaminated droplets or bodily fluids are transferred from an infected person.</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Symptoms include cold-like symptoms such as: loss of appetite, headache, fatigue, irritability, cough,&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">a moderately high temperature, a non-itchy red rash and painful mouth ulcers. Hand, foot and mouth&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">disease may cause all of the above signs and symptoms or just a few of them. Please seek immediate&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">medical advice and advise the school promptly if your child is unwell with any of the above symptoms.</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">At school, we are taking all precautions necessary including:</font></div><div><ul><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">Ensuring all classrooms are disinfected with both ultra-violet light and a disinfectant</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">Good ventilation of classrooms and other rooms</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">Daily cleaning and disinfection of the door handles, stair railings, toys, bathroom accessories&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">and food utensils</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">Early Yearsâ€™ toys thoroughly disinfected every Friday</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">Unwell children will see nurse and if necessary parents will be contacted</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">The children have been taught how to wash their hands by teachers</span></li></ul></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">If you believe your child has hand, foot and mouth disease, please seek medical treatment, follow&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">safety procedures at home and keep them away from school until they have recovered from the&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">illness.</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">For further information about hand, foot and mouth disease, please <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/hand-foot-and-mouth-disease/Pages/Introduction.aspx">follow this link</a>.</font></div><div><br></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Kind Regards</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Alison Mackey</font></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Deputy Head of Primary</font></span></div></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><p dir="ltr" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><br></p><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</span></div></div></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
